      "titleBosnian": "AirPods Pro 3",
      "titleEnglish": "AirPods Pro 3",
      "teaserBosnian": "Kada je u pitanju audio oprema, AirPods Pro 3 postavlja nove standarde kvalitete zvuka i dizajna. Ovaj proizvod je rezultat godina istraživanja i razvoja, s ciljem da pruži audiofili i casual slušaocima podjednako zadovoljavajuće iskustvo. Sa Bluetooth 5.3, zvuk je kristalno čist, sa dubokim basovima i preciznim visokim tonovima koji oživljavaju svaku nijansu vaše omiljene muzike.",
      "teaserEnglish": "When it comes to audio equipment, AirPods Pro 3 sets new standards in sound quality and design. This product is the result of years of research and development, with the aim of providing audiophiles and casual listeners alike with a satisfying experience. With Bluetooth 5.3, the sound is crystal clear, with deep bass and precise highs that bring every nuance of your favorite music to life.",
