      "teaserEnglish": "ROG Phone 9 Pro represents the pinnacle of modern design and technological innovation in the smartphone category. This device has been carefully designed to meet the needs of the most demanding users, combining powerful performance with elegant design. Thanks to a 6.78\" AMOLED 185Hz display, ROG Phone 9 Pro offers an experience that will transform the way you use technology in your daily life.",
