      "teaserEnglish": "Peripherals make the difference between a good and a great user experience, and the Logitech MX Master 3S is proof of that. This product is designed with one goal in mind – to give you maximum control and comfort at every moment of use. The 8K DPI sensor ensures precision and responsiveness that will satisfy even the most professional users.",
